{"tid":427704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU怕醜襲台撐GD A Pink攰爆抵台逾200粉絲接機","createTime":"2017-10-07T15:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T12:30:24.000Z","uid":34643,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e41fc25d2867919ad22ff22bf66507b29e741adc","tid":427704,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"韓國6人女團A Pink上月來港喺亞博館舉行《2017 Apink Asia Tour [Pink UP] in Hong Kong》演唱會，當時因為安全檢查問題令演唱會延遲80分鐘先開始。<br />\n<br />\n而聽日A Pink就會移師到台灣開騷，佢哋今日就先抵台做準備，雖然航班比較早，但仍吸引數名粉絲喺閘內等候佢哋，又送上禮物給偶像，出到閘口更有逾200名粉絲接機，場面墟冚。顯得一臉倦容嘅A Pink見到粉絲咁熱情都來者不拒，一一收下禮物，亦有企定定畀傳媒拍照。<br />\n另外，台灣本周有唔少韓星襲台搵銀，除咗A Pink外，噚晚同今晚就有Wanna One開見面會，今晚同後晚有BIGBANG嘅G-DRAGON開騷，聽日亦有南柱赫搞見面會，認真熱鬧。「國民妹妹」IU將擔任GD演唱會嘅嘉賓，IU今午抵台，行VIP通道，身穿粉紫色上衣嘅IU見到傳媒勁怕醜，不時掩嘴而笑，不過佢都好大方收粉絲嘅禮物。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171007/large/1507349328_90b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171007%2Flarge%2F1507349328_90b9.jpg&h=4b00ad8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171007/large/1507349329_d0bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171007%2Flarge%2F1507349329_d0bd.jpg&h=eb9f023f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLg3-PiUIAAizYN.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLg3-PiUIAAizYN.jpg%3Aorig&h=d4dc4c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLg34XuVAAQprJe.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLg34XuVAAQprJe.jpg%3Aorig&h=80208205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLgq1m9VYAAzxwo.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLgq1m9VYAAzxwo.jpg%3Aorig&h=f59eba87&s={SIZE}